data.description: Prime Location Alert! This residence boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. It is situated just south of the I-10 freeway, just minutes away from Eglin Air Force Base. Nestled in the desirable Countryview Estates neighborhood, it offers convenient access to PJ Adams and Antioch Rd. Upon entering, you will notice fresh paint on the walls, new blinds. New flooring in primary bathroom, hallway and living area. You will discover a generously sized living area with a door leading to a fenced backyard. Picture yourself enjoying a cup of coffee sitting by the charming bay window in the eat-in kitchen, which also boasts ample cabinet and counter space. The spacious master suite features an ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, a relaxing garden tub and a substantial walk-in closet! Roof replaced on 2021 Fun fact about this property: It offers the perfect opportunity for investors or homeowners seeking rental income. This lovely house boasts a unique layout with a separate, equipped living space on one side, ideal for generating rental revenue. The attached rental unit provides a private entrance, a bathroom, a comfortable bedroom, and the possibility to install a kitchen. With its proximity to schools, military bases, parks, and shopping, this property is not only a fantastic place to call home but also a smart investment for those looing to harness the potential of rental income.
